T1  - Age and entrepreneurial career success: A review and a meta-analysis
AU  - Zhao, Hao
AU  - O'Connor, Gina
AU  - Wu, Jihong
AU  - Lumpkin, G.T.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 36
